\nw[Mercenary Captain]Welcome back. Your sparring partner is in the
training ground behind you.
\nw[Mercenary Captain]Once you're ready, please start the mock battle.

Complete Quest [MockBattleApplication2]: Engage in
a mock battle with the mercenaries!!

\nw[Mercenary Captain]The mercenaries who will have a mock battle with
you are in the training grounds, just like last
time. When you're ready, please talk to the
mercenaries over there.

\nw[Mercenary]Did you come for a mock battle? I don't often have
the opportunity to fight against people, since I
mostly deal with monsters. I appreciate your help.

\nw[Mercenary]Oh, you've come for another mock battle, huh? I
hope we can build a good relationship for the
future.

\nw[Mercenary]Oh, you've come again. I'll be counting on you
from now on too.

\nw[Mercenary]A cute girl entered that shop. You'll definitely
like her too.

\nw[Mercenary]There's even a mercenary group with cute girls...
I'm so jealous...!

\nw[Mercenary]That shop has a really hot girl with a great body.
You should check it out next time.

\nw[Mercenary]Oh, so you're from the mercenary group that came
last time...

\nw[Mercenary]It seems you've come again. Are you ready for the
mock battle?
\nw[Mercenary]I see... Some are harder to affect...
パーティ２の場合変数193に１０を入れる
それによってパーティ２の値を参照する。
入れない場合はパーティ１の値を参照している。
Obtained a reward of 2000 EXP, 2000G, and 4 fame.
\nw[Mercenary]I see. Let me know when you're ready.
\nw[Mercenary]Hmm, so you guys are my opponents...
\nw[Mercenary]I have no intention of holding back.
There is no need to leave from here now.
\nw[Mercenary]Hmm, so you guys are my opponents...
